&lt;p id="k3WWcz"&gt;But now, Google says “technology has evolved dramatically” since the launch of the original &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2013/7/29/4566718/google-chromecast-review"&gt;Chromecast in 2013&lt;/a&gt;. “We invested heavily in embedding Google Cast technology into millions of TV devices, including Android TV,” Google writes. “We are taking the next step in evolving how streaming TV devices...&lt;/p&gt;
